room_title: Escape room "Creature of the Year" by Cluemaster Escape Rooms in Phoenix
room_description: Ms. Baker’s reputation precedes her - students love her and teachers strive to be her. She’s perfect… maybe, too perfect. Now, your classmates have suspiciously disappeared the week before summer. As the only students left, you sneak into class before school to get to the bottom of it all… but don’t get caught in her classroom, your life may depend on it.
